 The (detailed description of exactly what is required) of the weights matrix is a matter of some randomness and is often referred to as a major 
 weakness of the (something made of crossed strips of wood, metal, etc.) approach. A range of suggestions have been offered in the books, based on closeness, distance, as well as more general numbers.23 
